# On Canvas frame editing

The frame editing should be enahnced by allowing all or most frame manipulation should be available from the canvas.

The following manipulation exist in Scribus:

- move
- resize
- rotate
- edit nodes

On top of it, some or all manipulation should be available while being in edit mode.

Tasks:
- Enable frame rotation.
- Define a way to move the frame without clicking on its content (using the border?).
- Allow frame operations while in edit mode.
- Allow node editing wihtout using the palette.
